summary: My personal Idea of what Aela should look like, not lore friendly!!! But.. I still like it better than the vanilla one.
descriptionHtml:
Feel free to change this mod anyway you want, I have it set the way I like it but I can understand that some may like it with different colors or whatnot.

The following list are the mods needed to get this to work. Im not on here very much lately but if anyone has any problems feel free to ask me. ALSO you will probably need to load the mod in CK and do the cntrl-F4 on Aela to export the correct looking face, may be dark otherwise. Please endorse if you like her so she will get to the top of the list for others to see!

-ApachiiSkyHair - ApachiiSkyHair_v_1_4_Full
